      "doNotMiss": [
        "In a difficult RSI scenario, if the patient desaturates, gentle low-pressure mask ventilation (< 20 cmH2O) should be initiated to prevent hypoxic arrest (modified RSI)"
      ],
      "whenToEscalate": [
