        "Baseline severity of pre-existing diabetic peripheral neuropathy"
      ],
      "likelyClinicalCategoriesToConsider": [
        "Ankle Multimodal Pain Management",
        "Saphenous Nerve Sparing and Coverage",
        "Diabetic Regional Anesthesia Safety"
      ],
      "suggestedNextStepsGeneral": [
        "Locate the sciatic nerve bifurcation and the adjacent popliteal vessels under ultrasound in the distal thigh.",
        "Advance the needle within the paraneural sheath just proximal to the bifurcation and observe circumferential fluid spread.",
        "Perform a supplemental saphenous nerve block if medial coverage is necessary."
      ],
      "relatedAlgorithms": [
