      "conversationalText": "💉 Reconstitute each 20 mg vial of Dantrolene with exactly 60 mL of sterile water for injection. Do not use physiological saline (0.9% NaCl) or dextrose, as this will cause precipitation of the active compound. Administer initial dose of 2.5 mg/kg IV bolus, repeat every 5-10 minutes until crisis resolves.",
