      "conversationalText": "🔄 Prior to surgical cricothyroidotomy, alternative rescue interventions include supraglottic airway device insertion (e.g. LMA/i-gel), a final intubation attempt using a videolaryngoscope, or temporary needle cricothyroidotomy (with high-pressure jet ventilation).",
