    "en": {
      "safetyLevel": "routine",
      "notASubstituteWarning": "This response does not replace clinical judgment.",
      "conversationalText": "⚠️ There are no absolute contraindications to epinephrine in severe systemic anaphylaxis. While caution is advised in elderly patients, severe coronary artery disease, or uncontrolled hypertension, reversing distributive shock and airway obstruction remains the absolute life-saving priority.",
