      "conversationalText": "⚠️ **Congenital Diaphragmatic Hernia (CDH)** is an absolute contraindication to bag-mask ventilation! Positive pressure via mask inflates the herniated bowel in the thorax, causing fatal lung compression. The infant must be endotracheally intubated immediately at birth.",
