      "notASubstituteWarning": "This response does not replace clinical judgment.",
      "conversationalText": "🚨 Potential complications include pneumothorax (barotrauma) due to excessive ventilation pressures, gastric insufflation (aspiration risk), selective bronchial intubation, and liver laceration during poorly placed chest compressions.",
