      "conversationalText": "🩸 Upon activation, the blood bank issues packages of 6 units PRBCs, 6 units FFP, and 1 pool of Platelets. Infuse all products through rapid warmer devices. Administer 1 g of Calcium Gluconate IV after every 4 units of blood products to prevent citrate toxicity (hypocalcemia).",
