      "safetyLevel": "routine",
      "notASubstituteWarning": "This response does not replace clinical judgment.",
      "conversationalText": "🚨 Complications include TACO (circulatory overload), TRALI (acute lung injury), hypocalcemia from citrate binding, hyperkalemia (especially with older blood), hypothermia, hemolytic transfusion reactions, and severe hypotension. Monitor core temperature and ionized calcium continuously.",
